---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section id="local-community-component">
<div id="community-component" class="community-component">
    <div class="line-divider"></div>
    <div class="title-row">
        <h1>Lokale fælleskaber</h1>
        <div class="line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="paraghraph-container">
        <p>DFUNK er intet uden vores fantastiske community! Vores lokale fællesskaber er derfor en grundsten i vores organisation og arbejde. Uanset om det handler om fællesspisning i Madmekka eller vores volleyballhold, skaber vi stærke fællesskaber og bånd, der føles som en familie.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="link-component">
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/dfunkdk/" class="instagram-link">
            <img src="/icons/instagram-logo.png" alt="Instagram logo" class="insta-logo" /> Find os på Instagram
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="image-container">
        <img src="/fælleskab.png" alt="fælleskab" class="fælleskab-image" />
    </div>
</div> 
</section>



<style>
    .community-component {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 10px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin-top: 150px;
    width: 100%; /* Full width */
}

.line-divider {
    height: 2px; /* Thickness of the line */
    background: #FA4B00; /* Color of the line */
    width: 100%; /* Full width of the parent container */
    margin: 0 20px; 
    margin-bottom: 120px;
}

.title-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    color: #F0F0F0;
    width: 100%; 
    box-sizing: border-box;
    flex-wrap: wrap; /* Allow wrapping for smaller screens */
}

.title-row h1 {
   margin: 0;
    font-size: var(--font-size-large);
    font-weight: bolder;
}

.line {
    height: 2px;
    background: #F0F0F0;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 460px;
    margin: 0 20px;
}

.paraghraph-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #F0F0F0;
    padding: 40px;
    font-size: 1.2em; 
    text-align: start; 
    line-height: 40px;
}


.fælleskab-image {
    max-width: 100%; /* Ensure the image does not overflow its container */
    height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-top: 20px; /* Space above the image */
}

.link-component {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items:center;
    color: #F0F0F0;
    width: 84%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-size: 1.4em; /* Relative font size */
}

.instagram-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 1em;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: background-color 0.3s;
    max-width: 300px;
}

.insta-logo {
    width: 40px;
    height: auto;
    margin-right: 10px;
}

/* Responsive Breakpoints */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .title-row {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .line {
        max-width: 100%;
        margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .paraghraph-container {
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 1em;
    }


    .link-component {
        font-size: 1.2em;
        margin-top: 50px;
    }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
    .title-row h1 {
        font-size: 4vw; /* Increase size for small screens */
    }

    .button-link {
        padding: 8px 16px;
        font-size: 1em;
    }
}

    
    </style>